{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":160,"text":"Today, I'd like to talk with you"},{"time":1880,"text":"about something that should be\na totally uncontroversial topic."},{"time":7200,"text":"But, unfortunately,\nit's become incredibly controversial."}]},{"cues":[{"time":13200,"text":"This year, if you think about it,"},{"time":15440,"text":"over a billion couples\nwill have sex with one another."},{"time":19640,"text":"Couples like this one,"},{"time":22200,"text":"and this one,"},{"time":23960,"text":"and this one,"},{"time":25440,"text":"and, yes,"},{"time":27080,"text":"even this one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":28320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":30240,"text":"And my idea is this --"},{"time":32640,"text":"all these men and women\nshould be free to decide"},{"time":37200,"text":"whether they do or do not\nwant to conceive a child."},{"time":41680,"text":"And they should be able to use\none of these birth control methods"},{"time":45160,"text":"to act on their decision."},{"time":49040,"text":"Now, I think you'd have a hard time"},{"time":51920,"text":"finding many people\nwho disagree with this idea."},{"time":56240,"text":"Over one billion people use birth control\nwithout any hesitation at all."},{"time":63400,"text":"They want the power\nto plan their own lives"},{"time":67560,"text":"and to raise healthier, better educated\nand more prosperous families."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74200,"text":"But, for an idea that is\nso broadly accepted in private,"},{"time":80360,"text":"birth control certainly generates\na lot of opposition in public."},{"time":85520,"text":"Some people think\nwhen we talk about contraception"},{"time":88960,"text":"that it's code for abortion,"},{"time":91040,"text":"which it's not."},{"time":92720,"text":"Some people -- let's be honest --"},{"time":95120,"text":"they're uncomfortable with the topic\nbecause it's about sex."},{"time":99320,"text":"Some people worry"},{"time":101080,"text":"that the real goal of family planning\nis to control populations."},{"time":106720,"text":"These are all side issues"},{"time":110560,"text":"that have attached themselves\nto this core idea that men and women"},{"time":116360,"text":"should be able to decide\nwhen they want to have a child."},{"time":121240,"text":"And as a result, birth control has\nalmost completely and totally disappeared"},{"time":127840,"text":"from the global health agenda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130280,"text":"The victims of this paralysis\nare the people of sub-Saharan Africa"},{"time":136520,"text":"and South Asia."},{"time":139040,"text":"Here in Germany, the proportion of people\nthat use contraception"},{"time":143440,"text":"is about 66 percent."},{"time":145200,"text":"That's about what you'd expect."},{"time":147960,"text":"In El Salvador, very similar, 66 percent."},{"time":151920,"text":"Thailand, 64 percent."},{"time":155440,"text":"But let's compare that to other places,"},{"time":157800,"text":"like Uttar Pradesh,\none of the largest states in India."},{"time":161520,"text":"In fact, if Uttar Pradesh\nwas its own country,"},{"time":165320,"text":"it would be the fifth largest\ncountry in the world."},{"time":169840,"text":"Their contraception rate -- 29 percent."},{"time":174200,"text":"Nigeria, the most populous\ncountry in Africa, 10 percent."},{"time":180680,"text":"Chad, 2 percent."},{"time":185640,"text":"Let's just take one country\nin Africa, Senegal."},{"time":188800,"text":"Their rate is about 12 percent."}]},{"cues":[{"time":190880,"text":"But why is it so low?"},{"time":193400,"text":"One reason is that the most popular\ncontraceptives are rarely available."},{"time":199560,"text":"Women in Africa will tell you\nover and over again"},{"time":202480,"text":"that what they prefer today\nis an injectable."},{"time":205600,"text":"They get it in their arm --\nand they go about four times a year,"},{"time":209640,"text":"they have to get it every three months --\nto get their injection."},{"time":212720,"text":"The reason women like it so much in Africa\nis they can hide it from their husbands,"},{"time":218600,"text":"who sometimes want a lot of children."},{"time":221280,"text":"The problem is every other time\na woman goes into a clinic in Senegal,"},{"time":226800,"text":"that injection is stocked out."},{"time":229440,"text":"It's stocked out 150 days out of the year."},{"time":234400,"text":"So can you imagine the situation --"},{"time":236280,"text":"she walks all this way\nto go get her injection."},{"time":239200,"text":"She leaves her field,\nsometimes leaves her children,"},{"time":242400,"text":"and it's not there."},{"time":243880,"text":"And she doesn't know\nwhen it's going to be available again."},{"time":247440,"text":"This is the same story\nacross the continent of Africa today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252880,"text":"And so what we've created as a world\nhas become a life-and-death crisis."},{"time":257519,"text":"There are 100,000 women [per year]\nwho say they don't want to be pregnant"},{"time":263720,"text":"and they die in childbirth --\n100,000 women a year."},{"time":268080,"text":"There are another 600,000 women [per year]"},{"time":270520,"text":"who say they didn't want to be pregnant\nin the first place,"},{"time":273360,"text":"and they give birth to a baby"},{"time":275480,"text":"and her baby dies\nin that first month of life."},{"time":279840,"text":"I know everyone wants to save\nthese mothers and these children."},{"time":286800,"text":"But somewhere along the way,\nwe got confused by our own conversation."},{"time":292640,"text":"And we stopped trying to save these lives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":297160,"text":"So if we're going to make\nprogress on this issue,"},{"time":300640,"text":"we have to be really clear\nabout what our agenda is."},{"time":304880,"text":"We're not talking about abortion."},{"time":307240,"text":"We're not talking\nabout population control."},{"time":310640,"text":"What I'm talking about is giving women\nthe power to save their lives,"},{"time":317160,"text":"to save their children's lives"},{"time":319280,"text":"and to give their families\nthe best possible future."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324080,"text":"Now, as a world,"},{"time":325960,"text":"there are lots of things we have to do\nin the global health community"},{"time":329240,"text":"if we want to make the world\nbetter in the future --"},{"time":332360,"text":"things like fight diseases."},{"time":334160,"text":"So many children today die of diarrhea,\nas you heard earlier, and pneumonia."},{"time":338720,"text":"They kill literally\nmillions of children a year."},{"time":341360,"text":"We also need to help small farmers --"},{"time":343480,"text":"farmers who plow\nsmall plots of land in Africa --"},{"time":348000,"text":"so that they can grow enough food\nto feed their children."},{"time":350920,"text":"And we have to make sure that\nchildren are educated around the world."},{"time":355040,"text":"But one of the simplest\nand most transformative things we can do"},{"time":360360,"text":"is to give everybody access\nto birth control methods"},{"time":364240,"text":"that almost all Germans have access to\nand all Americans, at some point,"},{"time":369720,"text":"they use these tools during their life."},{"time":373000,"text":"And I think as long as we're really clear\nabout what our agenda is,"},{"time":379120,"text":"there's a global movement\nwaiting to happen"},{"time":381760,"text":"and ready to get behind\nthis totally uncontroversial idea."}]},{"cues":[{"time":388480,"text":"When I grew up,\nI grew up in a Catholic home."},{"time":391800,"text":"I still consider myself\na practicing Catholic."},{"time":395280,"text":"My mom's great-uncle was a Jesuit priest."},{"time":399400,"text":"My great-aunt was a Dominican nun."},{"time":402840,"text":"She was a schoolteacher\nand a principal her entire life."},{"time":406600,"text":"In fact, she's the one who taught me\nas a young girl how to read."},{"time":411040,"text":"I was very close to her."},{"time":413280,"text":"And I went to Catholic schools\nfor my entire childhood"},{"time":416520,"text":"until I left home to go to university."},{"time":419800,"text":"In my high school, Ursuline Academy,"},{"time":423200,"text":"the nuns made service and social justice\na high priority in the school."},{"time":430080,"text":"Today, in the [Gates] Foundation's work,"},{"time":432440,"text":"I believe I'm applying the lessons\nthat I learned in high school."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438120,"text":"So, in the tradition of Catholic scholars,"},{"time":441040,"text":"the nuns also taught us\nto question received teachings."},{"time":447200,"text":"And one of the teachings that we girls\nand my peers questioned"},{"time":452480,"text":"was is birth control really a sin?"},{"time":457400,"text":"Because I think one of the reasons"},{"time":459160,"text":"we have this huge discomfort\ntalking about contraception"},{"time":463520,"text":"is this lingering concern"},{"time":465520,"text":"that if we separate sex from reproduction,\nwe're going to promote promiscuity."},{"time":471560,"text":"And I think that's a reasonable question\nto be asked about contraception --"},{"time":475840,"text":"what is its impact on sexual morality?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":481160,"text":"But, like most women,"},{"time":482520,"text":"my decision about birth control\nhad nothing to do with promiscuity."},{"time":487840,"text":"I had a plan for my future.\nI wanted to go to college."},{"time":491320,"text":"I studied really hard in college,"},{"time":493680,"text":"and I was proud to be one of the very few\nfemale computer science graduates"},{"time":498440,"text":"at my university."},{"time":500280,"text":"I wanted to have a career,\nso I went on to business school"},{"time":503640,"text":"and I became one of the youngest\nfemale executives at Microsoft."}]},{"cues":[{"time":509040,"text":"I still remember, though,\nwhen I left my parents' home"},{"time":512159,"text":"to move across the country\nto start this new job at Microsoft."},{"time":516120,"text":"They had sacrificed a lot\nto give me five years of higher education."},{"time":522120,"text":"But they said, as I left home --"},{"time":523720,"text":"and I literally went down the front steps,\ndown the porch at home --"},{"time":527080,"text":"and they said,"},{"time":528320,"text":"\"Even though you've had\nthis great education,"},{"time":531400,"text":"if you decide to get married\nand have kids right away,"},{"time":536560,"text":"that's OK by us, too.\""},{"time":539080,"text":"They wanted me to do the thing\nthat would make me the very happiest."},{"time":544360,"text":"I was free to decide what that would be."},{"time":547320,"text":"It was an amazing feeling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":550680,"text":"In fact, I did want to have kids --"},{"time":554600,"text":"but I wanted to have them\nwhen I was ready."},{"time":558520,"text":"And so now, Bill and I have three."},{"time":562000,"text":"And when our eldest daughter was born,"},{"time":564960,"text":"we weren't, I would say,\nexactly sure how to be great parents."},{"time":568680,"text":"Maybe some of you know that feeling."},{"time":571240,"text":"And so we waited a little while\nbefore we had our second child."},{"time":575040,"text":"And it's no accident\nthat we have three children"},{"time":578720,"text":"that are spaced three years apart."},{"time":581600,"text":"Now, as a mother, what do I want\nthe very most for my children?"},{"time":587520,"text":"I want them to feel the way I did --"},{"time":590240,"text":"like they can do anything\nthey want to do in life."},{"time":596040,"text":"And so, what has struck me"},{"time":597680,"text":"as I've travelled the last decade\nfor the foundation around the world"},{"time":602280,"text":"is that all women want that same thing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":607520,"text":"Last year, I was in Nairobi, in the slums,\nin one called Korogocho --"},{"time":612480,"text":"which literally means when translated,\n\"standing shoulder to shoulder.\""},{"time":617880,"text":"And I spoke with this women's group\nthat's pictured here."},{"time":620920,"text":"And the women talked very openly\nabout their family life in the slums,"},{"time":625080,"text":"what it was like."},{"time":626520,"text":"And they talked quite intimately\nabout what they did for birth control."},{"time":630920,"text":"Marianne, in the center of the screen\nin the red sweater,"},{"time":634080,"text":"she summed up that entire\ntwo-hour conversation"},{"time":637840,"text":"in a phrase that I will never forget."},{"time":641240,"text":"She said, \"I want to bring\nevery good thing to this child"},{"time":648520,"text":"before I have another.\""},{"time":651120,"text":"And I thought -- that's it."},{"time":653200,"text":"That's universal."},{"time":655240,"text":"We all want to bring\nevery good thing to our children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":660960,"text":"But what's not universal is our ability\nto provide every good thing."},{"time":665960,"text":"So many women suffer\nfrom domestic violence."},{"time":668680,"text":"And they can't even\nbroach the subject of contraception,"},{"time":671760,"text":"even inside their own marriage."},{"time":674240,"text":"There are many women\nwho lack basic education."},{"time":677840,"text":"Even many of the women\nwho do have knowledge and do have power"},{"time":683440,"text":"don't have access to contraceptives."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686120,"text":"For 250 years, parents around the world"},{"time":691160,"text":"have been deciding\nto have smaller families."},{"time":694960,"text":"This trend has been steady\nfor a quarter of a millennium,"},{"time":699160,"text":"across cultures and across geographies,"},{"time":702800,"text":"with the glaring exception\nof sub-Saharan Africa and South Asia."},{"time":709920,"text":"The French started bringing down\ntheir family size in the mid-1700s."},{"time":714400,"text":"And over the next 150 years,\nthis trend spread all across Europe."},{"time":721000,"text":"The surprising thing to me,\nas I learned this history,"},{"time":724600,"text":"was that it spread not along socioeconomic\nlines but around cultural lines."},{"time":731440,"text":"People who spoke the same language\nmade that change as a group."},{"time":735320,"text":"They made the same choice\nfor their family,"},{"time":737920,"text":"whether they were rich\nor whether they were poor."},{"time":742400,"text":"The reason that trend\ntoward smaller families spread"},{"time":745640,"text":"was that this whole way\nwas driven by an idea --"},{"time":749320,"text":"the idea that couples\ncan exercise conscious control"},{"time":754360,"text":"over how many children they have."},{"time":757640,"text":"This is a very powerful idea."},{"time":761680,"text":"It means that parents have\nthe ability to affect the future,"},{"time":766400,"text":"not just accept it as it is."}]},{"cues":[{"time":770960,"text":"In France, the average family size\nwent down every decade"},{"time":775040,"text":"for 150 years in a row\nuntil it stabilized."},{"time":779440,"text":"It took so long back then because\nthe contraceptives weren't that good."},{"time":784480,"text":"In Germany, this transition started\nin the 1880s, and it took just 50 years"},{"time":790720,"text":"for family size\nto stabilize in this country."},{"time":794120,"text":"And in Asia and Latin America,\nthe transition started in the 1960s,"},{"time":798760,"text":"and it happened much faster\nbecause of modern contraception."}]},{"cues":[{"time":805160,"text":"I think, as we go through this history,\nit's important to pause for a moment"},{"time":811000,"text":"and to remember why this has become\nsuch a contentious issue."},{"time":816080,"text":"It's because some family planning programs"},{"time":818760,"text":"resorted to unfortunate incentives\nand coercive policies."},{"time":824480,"text":"For instance, in the 1960s, India\nadopted very specific numeric targets"},{"time":831360,"text":"and they paid women to accept\nhaving an IUD placed in their bodies."},{"time":836200,"text":"Now, Indian women were\nreally smart in this situation."},{"time":839600,"text":"When they went to get an IUD inserted,\nthey got paid six rupees."},{"time":843120,"text":"And so what did they do?"},{"time":844960,"text":"They waited a few hours or a few days,"},{"time":847000,"text":"and they went to another service provider\nand had the IUD removed for one rupee."},{"time":854200,"text":"For decades in the United States,"},{"time":857280,"text":"African-American women\nwere sterilized without their consent."},{"time":862880,"text":"The procedure was so common"},{"time":865120,"text":"it became known as\nthe Mississippi appendectomy --"},{"time":869200,"text":"a tragic chapter in my country's history."},{"time":873400,"text":"And as recently as the 1990s, in Peru,"},{"time":876200,"text":"women from the Andes region\nwere given anesthesia"},{"time":879720,"text":"and they were sterilized\nwithout their knowledge."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884200,"text":"The most startling thing about this"},{"time":886840,"text":"is that these coercive policies\nweren't even needed."},{"time":889600,"text":"They were carried out in places"},{"time":891440,"text":"where parents already\nwanted to lower their family size."},{"time":896120,"text":"Because in region after region,\nagain and again,"},{"time":899440,"text":"parents have wanted\nto have smaller families."},{"time":903600,"text":"There's no reason to believe"},{"time":905400,"text":"that African women\nhave innately different desires."},{"time":909520,"text":"Given the option,\nthey will have fewer children."},{"time":914080,"text":"The question is:"},{"time":915600,"text":"will we invest in helping\nall women get what they want now?"},{"time":921880,"text":"Or, are we going to condemn them\nto some century-long struggle,"},{"time":926600,"text":"as if this was still revolutionary France"},{"time":929360,"text":"and the best method\nwas coitus interruptus?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":935320,"text":"Empowering parents --\nit doesn't need justification."},{"time":940560,"text":"But here's the thing -- our desire\nto bring every good thing to our children"},{"time":947440,"text":"is a force for good throughout the world."},{"time":950640,"text":"It's what propels societies forward."},{"time":954600,"text":"In that same slum in Nairobi,\nI met a young businesswoman,"},{"time":958560,"text":"and she was making backpacks\nout of her home."},{"time":960800,"text":"She and her young kids\nwould go to the local jeans factory"},{"time":964160,"text":"and collect scraps of denim."},{"time":965920,"text":"She'd create these backpacks\nand resell them."},{"time":968480,"text":"And when I talked with her,\nshe had three children,"},{"time":970885,"text":"and I asked her about her family."},{"time":972485,"text":"And she said she and her husband decided"},{"time":974600,"text":"that they wanted to stop\nhaving children after their third one."},{"time":977640,"text":"And so when I asked her why,\nshe simply said,"},{"time":980320,"text":"\"Well, because I couldn't run\nmy business if I had another child.\""},{"time":983840,"text":"And she explained the income\nthat she was getting out of her business"},{"time":987103,"text":"afforded her to be able to give\nan education to all three of her children."},{"time":991280,"text":"She was incredibly optimistic\nabout her family's future."},{"time":997160,"text":"This is the same mental calculus"},{"time":999720,"text":"that hundreds of millions\nof men and women have gone through."},{"time":1003920,"text":"And evidence proves\nthat they have it exactly right."},{"time":1008320,"text":"They are able to give their children\nmore opportunities"},{"time":1012240,"text":"by exercising control\nover when they have them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1017280,"text":"In Bangladesh,"},{"time":1018600,"text":"there's a district called Matlab."},{"time":1020560,"text":"It's where researchers have collected data\non over 180,000 inhabitants since 1963."},{"time":1027319,"text":"In the global health community,"},{"time":1028880,"text":"we like to say it's one of the longest\npieces of research that's been running."},{"time":1032599,"text":"We have so many great health statistics."},{"time":1034800,"text":"In one of the studies, what did they do?"},{"time":1037359,"text":"Half the villagers\nwere chosen to get contraceptives."},{"time":1041480,"text":"They got education\nand access to contraception."},{"time":1044680,"text":"Twenty years later,\nfollowing those villages,"},{"time":1047880,"text":"what we learned is that they had a better\nquality of life than their neighbors."},{"time":1051920,"text":"The families were healthier."},{"time":1053640,"text":"The women were less likely\nto die in childbirth."},{"time":1056800,"text":"Their children were less likely\nto die in the first thirty days of life."},{"time":1060840,"text":"The children were better nourished."},{"time":1063160,"text":"The families were also wealthier."},{"time":1065200,"text":"The adult women's wages were higher."},{"time":1067720,"text":"Households had more assets --\nthings like livestock or land or savings."},{"time":1072800,"text":"Finally, their sons and daughters\nhad more schooling."},{"time":1077480,"text":"So when you multiply these types\nof effects over millions of families,"},{"time":1083440,"text":"the product can be large-scale\neconomic development."},{"time":1087560,"text":"People talk about the Asian\neconomic miracle of the 1980s --"},{"time":1091640,"text":"but it wasn't really a miracle."},{"time":1093720,"text":"One of the leading causes\nof economic growth across that region"},{"time":1097280,"text":"was this cultural trend\ntowards smaller families."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1102600,"text":"Sweeping changes start\nat the individual family level --"},{"time":1106520,"text":"the family making a decision\nabout what's best for their children."},{"time":1111760,"text":"When they make that change\nand that decision,"},{"time":1114800,"text":"those become sweeping\nregional and national trends."},{"time":1119160,"text":"When families in sub-Saharan Africa\nare given the opportunity"},{"time":1123320,"text":"to make those decisions for themselves,"},{"time":1126280,"text":"I think it will help spark\na virtuous cycle of development"},{"time":1129560,"text":"in communities across the continent."},{"time":1134000,"text":"We can help poor families\nbuild a better future."},{"time":1137880,"text":"We can insist that all people\nhave the opportunity"},{"time":1141600,"text":"to learn about contraceptives"},{"time":1143560,"text":"and have access\nto the full variety of methods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1148040,"text":"I think the goal here is really clear:"},{"time":1150920,"text":"universal access to birth control\nthat women want."},{"time":1156360,"text":"And for that to happen, it means that\nboth rich and poor governments alike"},{"time":1161680,"text":"must make contraception a total priority."},{"time":1165760,"text":"We can do our part,\nin this room and globally,"},{"time":1169760,"text":"by talking about the hundreds\nof millions of families"},{"time":1173040,"text":"that don't have access\nto contraception today"},{"time":1175960,"text":"and what it would do to change\ntheir lives if they did have access."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1180680,"text":"I think if Marianne\nand the members of her women's group"},{"time":1184440,"text":"can talk about this openly"},{"time":1186760,"text":"and have this discussion\nout amongst themselves and in public,"},{"time":1190800,"text":"we can, too."},{"time":1192760,"text":"And we need to start now."},{"time":1195480,"text":"Because like Marianne, we all want\nto bring every good thing to our children."},{"time":1202800,"text":"And where is the controversy in that?"},{"time":1206160,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1207400,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1210160,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thank you."},{"time":1218360,"text":"I have some questions for Melinda."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1222360,"text":"(Applause ends)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1223680,"text":"Thank you for your courage\nand everything else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1227480,"text":"So, Melinda, in the last few years"},{"time":1230000,"text":"I've heard a lot of smart people\nsay something to the effect of,"},{"time":1235400,"text":"\"We don't need to worry\nabout the population issue anymore."},{"time":1238880,"text":"Family sizes are coming down\nnaturally all over the world."},{"time":1242400,"text":"We're going to peak\nat nine or 10 billion. And that's it.\""},{"time":1246720,"text":"Are they wrong?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1247960,"text":"Melinda Gates: If you look\nat the statistics across Africa,"},{"time":1250760,"text":"they are wrong."},{"time":1252000,"text":"And I think we need to look at it,\nthough, from a different lens."},{"time":1255080,"text":"We need to look at it\nfrom the ground upwards."},{"time":1257280,"text":"I think that's one of the reasons\nwe got ourselves in so much trouble"},{"time":1260560,"text":"on this issue of contraception."},{"time":1262280,"text":"We looked at it from top down"},{"time":1263685,"text":"and said we want to have different\npopulation numbers over time."},{"time":1267240,"text":"Yes, we care about the planet.\nYes, we need to make the right choices."},{"time":1270560,"text":"But the choices have to be made\nat the family level."},{"time":1273160,"text":"And it's only by giving people access\nand letting them choose what to do"},{"time":1277520,"text":"that you get those sweeping changes\nthat we have seen globally --"},{"time":1280600,"text":"except for sub-Saharan Africa and those\nplaces in South Asia and Afghanistan."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1287920,"text":"CA: Some people on the right in America"},{"time":1290040,"text":"and in many conservative cultures\naround the world"},{"time":1295360,"text":"might say something like this:"},{"time":1297200,"text":"\"It's all very well to talk about saving\nlives and empowering women and so on."},{"time":1300891,"text":"But, sex is sacred."},{"time":1304000,"text":"What you're proposing\nis going to increase the likelihood"},{"time":1308040,"text":"that lots of sex happens outside marriage."},{"time":1310280,"text":"And that is wrong.\""},{"time":1312600,"text":"What would you say to them?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1314680,"text":"MG: I would say\nthat sex is absolutely sacred."},{"time":1317960,"text":"And it's sacred in Germany,\nand it's sacred in the United States,"},{"time":1321080,"text":"and it's sacred in France\nand so many places around the world."},{"time":1324200,"text":"And the fact that 98 percent of women\nin my country who are sexually experienced"},{"time":1329120,"text":"say they use birth control\ndoesn't make sex any less sacred."},{"time":1333320,"text":"It just means that they're getting\nto make choices about their lives."},{"time":1336600,"text":"And I think in that choice,"},{"time":1337920,"text":"we're also honoring\nthe sacredness of the family"},{"time":1340840,"text":"and the sacredness of the mother's life"},{"time":1343120,"text":"and the childrens' lives\nby saving their lives."},{"time":1345400,"text":"To me, that's incredibly sacred, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1348760,"text":"CA: So what is your foundation\ndoing to promote this issue?"},{"time":1353520,"text":"And what could people here\nand people listening on the web --"},{"time":1357560,"text":"what would you like them to do?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1359120,"text":"MG: I would say this --\njoin the conversation."},{"time":1361287,"text":"We've listed the website up here.\nJoin the conversation."},{"time":1365480,"text":"Tell your story about how contraception\nhas either changed your life"},{"time":1369320,"text":"or somebody's life that you know."},{"time":1371360,"text":"And say that you're for this."},{"time":1372765,"text":"We need a groundswell\nof people saying, \"This makes sense."},{"time":1375504,"text":"We've got to give all women access --\nno matter where they live.\""},{"time":1378920,"text":"And one of the things\nthat we're going to do"},{"time":1381040,"text":"is do a large event July 11 in London,"},{"time":1384240,"text":"with a whole host of countries,\na whole host of African nations,"},{"time":1387640,"text":"to all say we're putting this back\non the global health agenda."},{"time":1390800,"text":"We're going to commit resources to it,"},{"time":1392680,"text":"and we're going to do planning\nfrom the bottom up with governments"},{"time":1395840,"text":"to make sure that women are educated --"},{"time":1397960,"text":"so that if they\nwant the tool, they have it,"},{"time":1400440,"text":"and that they have\nlots of options available"},{"time":1402560,"text":"either through\ntheir local healthcare worker"},{"time":1404680,"text":"or their local community rural clinic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1407920,"text":"CA: Melinda, I'm guessing that some\nof those nuns who taught you at school"},{"time":1412520,"text":"are going to see\nthis TED Talk at some point."},{"time":1415960,"text":"Are they going to be horrified,\nor are they cheering you on?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1418880,"text":"MG: I know they're going\nto see the TED Talk"},{"time":1421000,"text":"because they know that I'm doing it\nand I plan to send it to them."},{"time":1424160,"text":"And, you know, the nuns who taught me\nwere incredibly progressive."},{"time":1427320,"text":"I hope that they'll be very proud of me"},{"time":1429240,"text":"for living out what they taught us\nabout social justice and service."},{"time":1433200,"text":"I have come to feel\nincredibly passionate about this issue"},{"time":1437120,"text":"because of what I've seen\nin the developing world."},{"time":1439920,"text":"And for me, this topic\nhas become very close to heart"},{"time":1444800,"text":"because you meet these women\nand they are so often voiceless."},{"time":1447880,"text":"And yet they shouldn't be --"},{"time":1449240,"text":"they should have a voice,\nthey should have access."},{"time":1451800,"text":"And so I hope they'll feel"},{"time":1453080,"text":"that I'm living out\nwhat I've learned from them"},{"time":1455920,"text":"and from the decades of work\nthat I've already done at the foundation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1460200,"text":"CA: So, you and your team brought together\ntoday an amazing group of speakers"},{"time":1464600,"text":"to whom we're all grateful."},{"time":1467680,"text":"Did you learn anything?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1469520,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1470760,"text":"MG: Oh my gosh, I learned so many things.\nI have so many follow-up questions."},{"time":1474600,"text":"And I think a lot\nof this work is a journey."},{"time":1476880,"text":"You heard the discussion\nabout the journey through energy,"},{"time":1480760,"text":"or the journey through social design,"},{"time":1483120,"text":"or the journey in the coming and saying,"},{"time":1485064,"text":"\"Why aren't there any women\non this platform?\""},{"time":1487240,"text":"And I think for all of us who work\non these development issues,"},{"time":1490640,"text":"you learn by talking to other people."},{"time":1492440,"text":"You learn by doing.\nYou learn by trying and making mistakes."},{"time":1495320,"text":"And it's the questions you ask."},{"time":1496840,"text":"Sometimes it's the questions you ask\nthat helps lead to the answer"},{"time":1500240,"text":"the next person\nthat can help you answer it."},{"time":1502360,"text":"So I have lots of questions\nfor the panelists from today."},{"time":1505080,"text":"And I thought it was just an amazing day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1507160,"text":"CA: Melinda, thank you for inviting\nall of us on this journey with you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1510518,"text":"Thank you so much.\nMG: Great. Thanks, Chris."}]}]}